description: Metrics from MyPerf4J stored in InfluxDB v1.x

targets.query:
from(bucket: v.bucket)
|> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
|> filter(fn: (r) => r.pool == "G1 Eden Space" and (r._field == "jvm_memory_pool_bytes_used" or r._field == "jvm_memory_pool_bytes_max"))
|> pivot(rowKey:["_time"], columnKey: ["_field"], valueColumn: "_value")
|> map(fn: (r) => ({ _time: r._time, _value: r.jvm_memory_pool_bytes_used / r.jvm_memory_pool_bytes_max * 100.0 }))

from(bucket: v.bucket)
|> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
|> filter(fn: (r) => r.pool == "G1 Survivor Space" and (r._field == "jvm_memory_pool_bytes_used" or r._field == "jvm_memory_pool_bytes_max"))
|> pivot(rowKey:["_time"], columnKey: ["_field"], valueColumn: "_value")
|> map(fn: (r) => ({ _time: r._time, _value: r.jvm_memory_pool_bytes_used / r.jvm_memory_pool_bytes_max * 100.0 }))

from(bucket: v.bucket)
|> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
|> filter(fn: (r) => r.area == "heap" and (r._field == "jvm_memory_bytes_used" or r._field == "jvm_memory_bytes_max"))
|> pivot(rowKey:["_time"], columnKey: ["_field"], valueColumn: "_value")
|> map(fn: (r) => ({ _time: r._time, _value: r.jvm_memory_bytes_used / r.jvm_memory_bytes_max * 100.0 }))

from(bucket: v.bucket)
|> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
|> filter(fn: (r) => r.area == "nonheap" and (r._field == "jvm_memory_bytes_used" or r._field == "jvm_memory_bytes_max"))
|> pivot(rowKey:["_time"], columnKey: ["_field"], valueColumn: "_value")
|> map(fn: (r) => ({ r with _value: r.jvm_memory_bytes_used / r.jvm_memory_bytes_max }))

from(bucket: v.bucket)
|> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
|> filter(fn: (r) => r.pool == "Metaspace" and (r._field == "jvm_memory_pool_bytes_used" or r._field == "jvm_memory_pool_bytes_max"))
|> pivot(rowKey:["_time"], columnKey: ["_field"], valueColumn: "_value")
|> map(fn: (r) => ({ r with _value: r.jvm_memory_pool_bytes_used / r.jvm_memory_pool_bytes_max }))

from(bucket: v.bucket)
    |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
    |> filter(fn: (r) => r._field == "java_lang_OperatingSystem_OpenFileDescriptorCount" or r._field == "java_lang_OperatingSystem_MaxFileDescriptorCount")
    |> pivot(rowKey:["_time"], columnKey: ["_field"], valueColumn: "_value")
    |> map(fn: (r) => ({ _time: r._time, _value: r.java_lang_OperatingSystem_OpenFileDescriptorCount / r.java_lang_OperatingSystem_MaxFileDescriptorCount * 100.0 }))
